: Personal data
                        collected, stored, used, and/or processed by AIHelp, as
                        described in this Privacy Notice, is handled in
                        accordance with Lei Geral de Proteção de Dados (LGPD).
                        By using or accessing our Sites or Services, individuals
                        expressly consent to the collection, use, storage, and
                        processing of their personal data by us for the purposes
                        detailed in this Notice.
Canada
: Personal data, as
                        defined in the Personal Information Protection and
                        Electronic Documents Act (PIPEDA), will be collected,
                        stored, used, and/or processed by AIHelp in compliance
                        with our obligations under PIPEDA.
