Your Rights:
Subject to limited exceptions under applicable law, you have the right to access your personal information and to update, correct or rectify such information if it is inaccurate, incomplete or no longer up to date. You also have the right to request information about the processing of your personal information, such as whether we hold such information about you, the purposes for which it is used, and the third parties with whom we may share your information, subject to applicable law.
